actions.description:
An API for measurement unit conversion. For each measurement class, you can convert from/to these units:'

-area: in ** 2, m ** 2, mi ** 2, meter ** 2, centimeter ** 2, yard ** 2, cm ** 2, ha, acre, ft ** 2, foot ** 2, km ** 2, yd ** 2, kilometer ** 2, inch ** 2, mile ** 2, hectare;

-digital: kilobit, gigabit, Gbit, TB, kbit, B, terabyte, megabit, megabyte, kB, GB, bit, kilobyte, gigabyte, terabit, byte, Tbit;

-energy: kilocalorie, kWh, Cal, dietary_calorie, kJ, calorie, kilowatt_hour, kcal, cal, J, joule, kilojoule;

-frequency: Hz, hertz, GHz, gigahertz, megahertz, kHz, kilohertz;

-length: pc, mile_scandinavian, meter, m, micrometer, yard, pm, centimeter, au, picometer, ly, light_year, cm, mi, ft, decimeter, dm, yd, inch, parsec, mile, millimeter, nanometer, foot, kilometer, µm, mm, in, nautical_mile, astronomical_unit, nmi, nm, km;

-mass: µg, t, metric_ton, gram, kilogram, g, mg, ct, microgram, ton, milligram, kg, ounce, pound, lb, oz, carat, troy ounce;

-angle: degree, deg, radian, arcminute, revolution, rad, arcsec, arcsecond, arcmin;

-speed: mi / h, kilometer / hour, mile / hour, m / s, meter / second, kt, km / h, knot;

-acceleration: m / s ** 2, meter / second ** 2, g_0, gravity;

-pressure: inHg, mmHg, psi, pound_force_per_square_inch, hectopascal, millimeter_Hg, mbar, inch_Hg, hPa, millibar;

-temperature: celsius, K, kelvin, °F, fahrenheit, °C;

-duration: s, ms, month, week, year, min, hour, century, ns, nanosecond, a, d, day, minute, h, millisecond, microsecond, µs, second;

-volume: kilometer ** 3, inch ** 3, deciliter, in ** 3, tbsp, cp, mi ** 3, floz, pint, mile ** 3, pt, yd ** 3, quart, tsp, l, centiliter, meter ** 3, metric_cup, hl, tablespoon, foot ** 3, megaliter, cl, acre_foot, yard ** 3, teaspoon, gallon, milliliter, m ** 3, centimeter ** 3, qt, km ** 3, fluid_ounce, cm ** 3, gal, hectoliter, dl, liter, ml, cup, ft ** 3;

-consumption: mi / gal, mile / gallon, liter / kilometer, l / km, liter_per_100kilometers;

-power: kW, milliwatt, megawatt, mW, watt, W, horsepower, kilowatt, hp.

